Package gobblin.data.management.retention.profile

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ConfigurableGlobDatasetFinder<T extends Dataset>
    A configurable DatasetsFinder that looks for CleanableDatasets using a glob pattern.
    GlobCleanableDatasetFinder
    Creates ConfigurableCleanableDataset from a glob for retention jobs.
    ManagedCleanableDatasetFinder
    A ConfigurableGlobDatasetFinder backed by gobblin-config-management.
    ModificationTimeDatasetProfile
    DatasetsFinder for ModificationTimeDatasets.
    MultiCleanableDatasetFinder
    A Clenable DatasetFinder that instantiates multiple DatasetFinders.
    MultiDatasetFinder
    A DatasetFinder that instantiates multiple DatasetFinders.
    ProxyableDatasetProfile
    A wrapper of ConfigurableGlobDatasetFinder that looks for data.management.retention.dataset.Datasets with FileSystems CleanableDatasets with FileSystems proxied as the owner of each dataset.
    SnapshotDatasetProfile
    DatasetsFinder for snapshot datasets.
    TrackingDatasetProfile
    DatasetsFinder for tracking datasets.
